.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# TeX build artifacts
*.aux
*.bcf
*.bbl
*.blg
*.fdb_latexmk
*.fls
*.glo
*.gls
*.idx
*.ilg
*.ind
*.log
*.out
*.run.xml
*.synctex.gz
*.toc
*.xref
*-blx.bib
*.hd

# Generated documents（编译生成的论文 PDF；封面资源见 figures/ 例外）
*.pdf
!figures/
!figures/**/*.pdf
# 可选：将示例/手册预编译 PDF 纳入版本库，便于「仅克隆」即可获得成品（需本地 make all 后提交）
!swuthesis-main.pdf
!swuthesis-graduate-main.pdf
!swuthesis-postdoc-main.pdf
!swuthesis-doc.pdf
swuthesis-main.bib
swuthesis-graduate-main.bib
swuthesis-postdoc-main.bib
